  "description": "<p>\n\t<img src=\"http://img.wdjimg.com/mms/icon/v1/b/7a/1b7ac6f8826971800db4c448dc1637ab_256_256.png\" /></p>\n<p>\n\t<a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p1012397\" title=\"点击获得更好的阅读体验\"><img src=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/2009/images/rss_video.gif\" /></a></p>\n<p>\n\tBobby Henrey is the child Phillipe and Ralph Richardson as Baines in the Fallen Idol from 1948. Deceptively simple, it's a memorable study of growing <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/childhood\" target=\"_blank\">childhood</a> <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/awareness\" target=\"_blank\">awareness</a> and adult <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/complicity\" target=\"_blank\">complicity</a> which won a Golden Globe, a BAFTA and three Oscar <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/nomination\" target=\"_blank\">nominations</a>. Newly restored, the film's to be re-released on DVD and Blu-ray, which gave me the excuse to talk to Robert Henrey who now lives in the United States. I asked him about the first time he knew about his audition for the Fallen Idol.</p>\n<p>\n\t&quot;I spent a lot of my childhood in Normandy with my grandmother, my French grandmother who would take care of me. And so I think the first thing I became aware of was my mother showing up and saying, you know, we're going to take a <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/flight\" target=\"_blank\">flight</a> and I'd never been on a plane before. So that was a kind of an exciting idea. We're gonna take a little plane and we're gonna go over to London for the day. And there are some people who want to talk to you, and it has to do with a film. I don't think any of that meant very much to me. I mean, I think the exciting part of it was that I was going to have the opportunity to get on a plane for the first time. We arrived at the other end, picked up in a car and we go to this rather grand office. Carol Reed was there, I mean, they were <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/obviously\" target=\"_blank\">obviously</a> other people, they were a whole team, and they asked me questions and took pictures and gave us lunch. I remember the lunch, that was a very important part of the whole thing. And you know, I was eight years old and really had no clear idea as to what was happening.&quot;&nbsp;</p>\n<p>\n\t<span>声明：音视频均来自互联网链接，仅供学习使用。本网站自身不存储、控制、修改被链接的内容。&ldquo;沪江</span><a>英语</a><span>&rdquo;高度重视知识产权保护。当如发现本网站发布的信息包含有侵犯其著作权的链接内容时，请联系我们，我们将依法采取措施移除相关内容或屏蔽相关链接。&gt;&gt;<a href=\"http://class.hujiang.com/course/52569?source=16553\" style=\"text-decoration: none; color: rgb(0, 90, 148);\" target=\"_blank\">零基础直达流利生活口语班</a>&lt;&lt;</span></p>\n<br /><center><a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p1012397/#relate_articles\"><img src=\"http://en.hujiang.com/2009/images/rss_chat.jpg\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a> <a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p1012397\"><img src=\"http://en.hujiang.com/2009/images/rss_digg.jpg\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a></center><h3 style=\"margin: 10px;\">本周最热文章</h3><ul style=\"margin: 5px 0;\"><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p1009856/\">Quora精选：高效人士有哪些好的日常行为？</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p835048/\">有声双语美文：没有任何一个行为不带后果</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p1011120/\">Quora精选：你有没有毫无用处的超能力？</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p1013754/\">4招让你更聪明地学习</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p997576/\">2017最值得一读的新书 中国作家的也入选了！</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p1013758/\">心理学家告诉你：四招识破一个说谎的人！</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p805845/\">2017新版《射雕英雄传》居然有8分！咋做到的</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p1